thread.title: Mote, Deborah
thread.title_full: Vacation Rental Pros reviewed by Mote, Deborah

author: Mote, Deborah
title: Mote, Deborah
text: Our 1BR rental was nice, comfortable and had all we needed...only complaint was a we had ~4-6 small bugs/roaches that we'd find each morning or through the day...could smell bug spray outside the building but inside either needed spraying or better caulking to keep them out. I would have preferred that the rental was closer to the beach but we were close to one of the pools and the guest house/gym facility.
